 0 0;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#111827;letter-spacing:-0.3px;line-height:1.2;">Critical: Action Item Severely Overdue</h1>\n<p style="margin:8px 0 0;font-size:15px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.5;">This item has been escalated due to severe delay.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td class="padding-mobile" style="padding:24px 44px 0;"><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">This action item is <strong style="color:#DC2626;">critically overdue</strong> and has been escalated for immediate resolution.</p></td></tr>\n\n<tr><td class="padding-mobile" style="padding:20px 44px 0;">\n<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background:#FEF2F2;border:2px solid #EF4444;border-radius:12px;">\n<tr><td style="padding:16px 20px;"><table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n<tr><td style="padding:4px 0"><span style="font-size:12px;color:#991B1B;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;">Action Item</span><br>\n<span style="font-size:14px;color:#7F1D1D;font-weight:600;">{{.ActionTitle}}</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td style="padding:4px 0"><span style="font-size:13px;color:#991B1B;">Was Due: <strong>{{.DueDate}}</strong> &middot; Days Overdue: <strong style="color:#DC2626;">{{.DaysOverdue}}</strong></span></td></tr>\n<tr><td style="padding:4px 0"><span style="font-size:13px;color:#991B1B;">Owner: <strong>{{.OwnerName}}</strong> &middot; Escalated To: <strong>{{.EscalateTo}}</strong></span></td></tr>\n<tr><td style="padding:4px 0"><span style="font-size:13px;color:#991B1B;">Related To: <strong>{{.RelatedEntity}}</strong></span></td></tr>\n</table></td></tr></table></td></tr>\n\n<tr><td class="padding-mobile" style="padding:16px 44px 0;">\n<p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">Please resolve this item immediately or provide a documented justification for the delay.</p></td></tr>\n\n<tr><td class="padding-mobile" style="padding:28px 44px 0;">\n<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"><tr><td align="center">\n<!--[if mso]><v:roundrect xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" href="{{.ActionURL}}" style="height:52px;v-text-anchor:middle;width:280px;" arcsize="15%" stroke="f" fillcolor="#991B1B"><w:anchorlock/><center><![endif]-->\n<a href="{{.ActionURL}}" target="_blank" style="display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#991B1B,#DC2626);color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:16px 48px;border-radius:12px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.2px;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(153,27,27,0.3),0 2px 6px rgba(153,27,27,0.3);mso-padding-alt:0;text-underline-color:#991B1B;">\n<!--[if mso]><i style="letter-spacing:48px;mso-font-width:-100%;mso-text-raise:24pt">&nbsp;</i><![endif]-->\n<span style="mso-text-raise:12pt;">Resolve Immediately &rarr;</span>\n<!--[if mso]><i style="letter-spacing:48px;mso-font-width:-100%">&nbsp;</i><![endif]-->\n</a><!--[if mso]></center></v:roundrect><![endif]-->\n</td></tr></table></td></tr>\n\n<tr><td class="padding-mobile" style="padding:20px 44px 0;">\n<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background:rgba(239,68,68,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.15);border-radius:10px;">\n<tr><td style="padding:12px 16px;"><table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n<tr><td style="vertical-align:middle;padding-right:10px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&#128680;</span></td>\n<td style="vertical-align:middle;"><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#991B1B;line-height:1.4;"><strong>ESCALATED</strong> &mdash; This item has been flagged for management review.</p></td></tr>\n</table></td></tr></table></td></tr>\n\n<tr><td class="padding-mobile" style="padding:28px 44px 0;">\n<div style="height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#e5e7eb 20%,#e5e7eb 80%,transparent);"></div></td